metadata.name: City Of Light
metadata.description:
There are magical rules in the cat palace. In this palace, only the royal family can become human. Princess Mia is the keeper of happiness from the royal family of cats, who uses a ring of light to bring happiness to the townspeople.
Sometimes she gets upset, in the meanwhile she is spending her time looking at people of the city to reclaim her energy to continue her duty as a person who is responsible for happiness.
